WEBVTT

00:00:29.937 --> 00:00:32.008
kwa kuongeza jeni 
zinazofanya isiwezekane

00:00:32.032 --> 00:00:34.746
kwa vimelea vya malaria 
kushindwa kuishi ndani ya mbu.

00:00:35.551 --> 00:00:37.373
lakini hiyo ilileta tatizo lingine.

00:00:38.043 --> 00:00:40.885
Sasa umeshapata
mbu asiyestahimili malaria,

00:00:40.909 --> 00:00:44.495
utamfanyaje aweze kubadilisha 
mbu wote wanaobeba malaria?

00:00:46.107 --> 00:00:47.580
Kuna chaguzi kadhaa,

00:00:47.604 --> 00:00:49.627
lakini mpango A ulikuwa wa uzalishaji

00:00:49.651 --> 00:00:52.738
kiasi cha mbu wapya 
waliotengenezwa kijenetiki

00:00:52.762 --> 00:00:54.088
waachilie mwituni

00:00:54.112 --> 00:00:56.079
na utegemee kwamba wataeneza jeni zao.

00:00:56.673 --> 00:00:58.787
Tatizo lilikuwa kwamba ulitakiwa uachilie

00:00:58.811 --> 00:01:03.111
kiasi cha mara 10 ya namba 
ya mbu wenyeji kufanyakazi